dct_title_s: Dawson's map of the Dominion of Canada 1881
dct_description_sm: Shows railroads existing and under construction, canals, counties, and civil townships.; Covers eastern Canada and part of northeastern United States.; Includes inset maps: Continuation of map to the Pacific, showing British Columbia & Manitoba -- Manitoba & connecting territory -- Environs of Montreal -- Newfoundland.; In lower right: "J. Bartholomew, Edinburgh."
